name: Fizz
title: the Tidal Trickster
shortBio: Fizz is an amphibious yordle, who dwells among the reefs surrounding Bilgewater. He often retrieves and returns the tithes cast into the sea by superstitious captains, but even the saltiest of sailors know better than to cross him—for many are the tales of those who have underestimated this slippery character. Often mistaken for some manner of capricious ocean spirit, he seems able to command the beasts of the deep, and delights in confounding his allies and enemies alike.

skins.name: Atlantean Fizz
skins.description: “When I was very young, my grandfather told me stories of Atlantis—of their high temples and great undersea army, and their great General Fizz. Grandfather remembered it as it was, you see, and not the silent mausoleum it has become.”

skins.name: Void Fizz
skins.description: There's no disputing that Fizz is a deadly creature of the endless Void. But even in the Void, Fizz is widely considered to be extremely irritating for his love of bringing life into existence just to annoy the Watchers.

skins.name: Cottontail Fizz
skins.description: Rising from the fluffiest depths to crush all root vegetable cohorts, Fizz commands the greatest threat carrots have ever known—a killer rabbit with the foulest and cruelest of tempers.

skins.name: Super Galaxy Fizz
skins.description: Nobody is quite sure how Fizz graduated the Super Galaxy academy, but one thing's for certain: no other pilot (or space fish) can summon a mecha-gigalodon from seemingly out of nowhere. Not that anyone should in the first place…

skins.name: Omega Squad Fizz
skins.description: Omega Squad's saboteur, Fizz is skilled in underwater combat. It is unclear what kind of action he saw before joining up, however, as he only ever refers to the sea as “a big bucket of chum.”

skins.name: Prestige Fuzz Fizz
skins.description: There's something deeply unnerving about a bipedal Cocker Spaniel mix running around society unchecked, stabbing pedestrians with a tennis ball grabber, and summoning other, bigger dogs out of the ground. And yet, here we all are. Together.

skins.description: Fizz defied all expectations when he successfully tamed an invader meep and resisted its corruption through their link. His unique connection promoted him to captain, a status he uses to pull mischievous pranks on his team. But when he's not tormenting his favorite lieutenant, he's unleashing his tricks on corrupted evildoers to keep planet M33P safe.

skins.name: Rain Shepherd Fizz

chromas.name: Rain Shepherd Fizz (Ruby)

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2024.

chromas.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2024.

skins.description: The fiendish Fizz was so jealous of the magical singing voices frogs possess that he taught himself how to sing and summon the rains. Though earsplitting at first, before long his songs were drawing tears from his listeners. With his magical vocals, Fizz is now keen to rain on everyone's parades.

passive.name: Nimble Fighter
passive.description: Fizz can move through units and takes a flat amount of reduced damage from all sources

spells.name: Urchin Strike
spells.description: Fizz dashes through his target, dealing magic damage and applying on hit effects.
spells.dynamicDescription: Fizz dashes through an enemy, dealing <physicalDamage>@TotalDamage@ physical damage</physicalDamage> plus <magicDamage>@QDamage@ magic damage</magicDamage>.@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@

spells.name: Seastone Trident
spells.description: Fizz's attacks bleed his enemies, dealing magic damage over several seconds. Fizz can empower his next attack to deal bonus damage and empower his further attacks for a short time.
spells.dynamicDescription:
Passive: Fizz's Attacks cause his enemies to bleed, dealing @DoTDamage@ magic damage over @BleedDuration@ seconds.

Active: Fizz's next Attack deals an additional @ActiveDamage@ magic damage. If this Attack kills its target, Fizz refunds @OnKillManaRefund@ Mana and reduces the cooldown of this Ability to @OnKillNewCooldown@ second. If it does not kill, Fizz's Attacks deal an additional @OnHitBuffDamage@ magic damage for @OnHitBuffDuration@ seconds.@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@

spells.name: Playful / Trickster
spells.description: Fizz hops into the air, landing gracefully upon his spear and becoming untargetable. From this position, Fizz can either slam the ground or choose to jump again before smashing back down.
spells.dynamicDescription:
Fizz hops onto his trident, becoming Untargetable for 0.75 seconds, after which he deals @EDamage@ magic damage to nearby enemies and Slows them by @SlowAmount*100@% for @SlowDuration@ seconds.

Fizz can Recast this Ability while Untargetable to dash again, which ends the effect early, deals damage in a smaller area, and doesn't Slow.@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@

spells.name: Chum the Waters
spells.description: Fizz tosses a fish in a direction that attaches to any champion that touches it, slowing the target. After a short delay, a shark erupts from the ground, knocking up the target and knocking any nearby enemies aside. All enemies hit are dealt magic damage and slowed.
spells.dynamicDescription:
Fizz launches a fish that attaches to the first champion hit. The victim is afflicted with True Sight and Slowed by between 40% to 80% based on how far the fish travelled before attaching.

After @DetonationTime@ seconds a shark erupts on the target, Knocking Up the target with the fish for 1 second, Knocking Back everything else, and dealing between @SmallSharkDamage@ to @BigSharkDamage@ magic damage based on how far the fish travelled before attaching.@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@
